{{main|Heroes of the Environment}} '''[[Heroes of the Environment]]''' is a list published in [[Time Magazine]]. The third list was published in September 2009.<ref name="timecover">[http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/completelist/0,29569,1924149,00.html Heroes of the Environment - TIME] - Cover story.</ref>
The list contains 30 entries, individuals or groups, that have contributed substantially to the preservation of [[Natural environment|environment]]. It is divided into four categories: Leaders & Visionaries, Activists, Scientists & Innovators and Moguls & Entrepreneurs.
