==Scientists and innovators== {{Div col|colwidth=30em}} *[[Takashi Yabe]] *[[Residency (domicile)|Residents]] of [[Vauban, Freiburg|Vauban]] *Valerie Casey *[[David Keith (scientist)]] *[[Bindeshwar Pathak]] *[[Olga Speranskaya]] *[[Pen Hadow]], Martin Hartley, and Ann Daniels *Nathan Lorenz and Tim Bauer {{div col end}}
==Moguls and entrepreneurs== {{Div col|colwidth=30em}} *[[Sheri Liao]] * Thomas Harttung *[[Dorjee Sun]] *Asim Buksh *Kin Lui, Raymond Ho and [[Casson Trenor]] *Yumi Someya * Bill Weihl, [[Google.org]]'s green energy czar {{div col end}}
